trans-unit.source: Identifies the reason for a Terminal Services session change.
trans-unit.target: Identifica o motivo para uma alteração de sessão de serviços de Terminal.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object is equal to the current session change description.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto especificado é igual a descrição da alteração de sessão atual.

trans-unit.source: The return value is `false` if `obj` is not a <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> or if it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: O valor de retorno é `false` se `obj` não é um <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription>ou se for `null`.</xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription>

trans-unit.source: Equality is determined by comparing the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the specified <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure to the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> properties of the current <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> structure.
trans-unit.target: Igualdade é determinada através da comparação a <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A>e <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A>Propriedades de especificado <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription>estrutura para o <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A>e <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A>Propriedades de atual <xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription>estrutura.</xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> </xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> </xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A> </xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription> </xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.SessionId%2A> </xref:System.ServiceProcess.SessionChangeDescription.Reason%2A>

trans-unit.source: The two structures are considered equal if their properties are equal.
trans-unit.target: As duas estruturas são consideradas igual se as respetivas propriedades são iguais.
